readme:
# Quizz

## Install

Add quizz to your *package.json*.

    npm install --save quizz

To instanciate a quizz

    var Manager = require("quizz").GameManager
    var m = new Manager()

    m.start()
    m.stop()

## Hubot

Provided with a [Hubot script!](misc/hubot-quizz.coffee)
